@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

I’d say put it in all three client under client.java & gui.java and search for serverip or ip and change it to 127.0.0.1 (host ip) or is it that your having trouble getting others to connect with your server? if so make a copy of the clients that have 127.0.0.1 ip and then if your going to release the client change the ips in the regular client folders to your serverip if this doesn’t work and others can’t get online you must have not portfoward correctly.
